milestones.description: Ian Billcliff and Joe Harris's 86-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Ian Billcliff and Joe Harris
Ashish Bagai and Sanjayan Thuraisingam's 24-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between Ashish Bagai and Sanjayan Thuraisingam
John Davison has broken the record for most sixes (2) in ODIs for CAN, going past Chumney's 1
John Davison has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (2) in ODIs for CAN, going past Mauricette's 1
Ian Billcliff has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (44) in an innings in ODIs for CAN, going past Ian Billcliff's 24
Sanjayan Thuraisingam has conceded the most runs in an innings (53) in ODIs for CAN, going past Davis Joseph's record of 42
Thomas Odoyo has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (53) for KENYA, going past Steve Tikolo
Ian Billcliff has become the top scorer for CAN in ODIs with 113 runs, going past Glenroy Sealy's 73
Ian Billcliff and Joe Harris's 86-run partnership is CAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 54 between Glenroy Sealy and Chappell
Ian Billcliff's 71 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for CAN), surpassing Glenroy Sealy's 45

stories.title: Kenya defeat brave Canada by four wickets
stories.summary: Kenya edged past Canada to win by four wickets with nine balls to spare, despite a late wobble as the Canadians exerted pressure, took vital wickets and so nearly pulled off another upset at this World Cup
